This software uses publicly available and official tools provided by Microsoft to optimize and repair the Windows operating system. To learn more about these tools, please refer to the official Microsoft documentation:

- [PowerShell](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/powershell/)
- [WMIC](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/win32/wmisdk/wmi-start-page)
- [DISM](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows-hardware/manufacture/desktop/dism-supported-platforms)
- [SFC](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows-server/administration/windows-commands/sfc)
- [CHKDSK](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows-server/administration/windows-commands/chkdsk)
- [Defrag](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows-server/administration/windows-commands/defrag)
- [Task Scheduler](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/win32/taskschd/task-scheduler-start-page)
